    <summary>A powerful command and plugin framework for .NET applications</summary>
    <description>
      Jiro.Commands is a comprehensive framework for building command-based applications with plugin support.
      It provides a robust foundation for creating extensible .NET applications with dynamic command loading,
      type-safe parameter parsing, and flexible result handling.

      Features:
      • Dynamic command registration and execution
      • Plugin-based architecture with hot-loading capabilities
      • Advanced parameter parsing with type conversion
      • Multiple result types (Text, JSON, Image, Graph)
      • Quote-aware command tokenization
      • Comprehensive error handling and validation
      • Full dependency injection support
      • XML documentation for excellent IntelliSense support
    </description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/HueByte/Jiro.Libs/blob/main/dev/docs/changelog/v$version$.md</releaseNotes>
    <copyright>Copyright © HueByte 2025</copyright>
    <tags>commands plugins framework dotnet csharp extensibility cli command-line</tags>

    <!-- Target Framework -->
